Yes it is possible to query the select search results by using filter property

Use like this:

&gt; In select component add filter property

    &lt;v-select
              v-model=&quot;activity.scs&quot;
              :items=&quot;statement&quot;
              item-text=&quot;name&quot;
              item-value=&quot;id&quot;
              label=&quot;Select&quot;
              persistent-hint
              :filter=&quot;selectFilter&quot;
              return-object
              multiple
              chips
              deletable-chips
              clearable
              counter
              filter
              &gt;
    &lt;/v-select&gt;  

&gt; in methods

    selectFilter(item, queryText) {   
      queryText = queryText.toLowerCase();
    
      return item.name.toLowerCase().indexOf(queryText) &gt; -1 || item.id.toLowerCase().indexOf(queryText) &gt; -1; 
    }

This way you can have custom filters to search on all the properties in your item object

