answers.body_markdown:
There is an error in the tutorial you were following. `location = ...` exactly matches a single URI, whereas you need to match all URIs below `/static/`.

Use:

    location = /favicon.ico { ... } 
    location /static/ { ... }
    location / { ... }

See [this document](http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_core_module.html#location) for details.

